Name: domino-spatial
Version: 0.1.5
Summary: DOMINO: diffusion-optimised graph learning identifies domain structures with enhanced accuracy and scalability
Home-page: https://github.com/ABILiLab/DOMINO
Author: Pan Jia, Wenjun Liu, Ning Liu, and Fuyi Li
Author-email: jiapan@nwafu.edu.cn; nora.liu@adelaide.edu.au; ning.liu@adelaide.edu.au; fuyi.li@nwafu.edu.cn
